'''''Star Wars Kids'' 11''' is the eleventh issue of [[Star Wars Kids (1997)|''Star Wars Kids'']] magazine. It was published by [[Scholastic]] and released in [[July]] [[1998]]. Issue 11 included part one of the serial [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] ''[[Imperial Spy]]'', written by [[Mike W. Barr]].

''Star Wars Kids'' 11 was available exclusively to subscribers of Scholastic's ''[[Star Wars Missions]]'' young-reader series and [[roleplaying game]], which arrived as monthly continuity packages via direct mail. Each package included a new ''Star Wars Kids'' magazine issue and the latest ''Star Wars Missions'' adventure book. ''Star Wars Kids'' 11 came packaged with the game's eleventh adventure book, [[Star Wars Missions 11: Bounty Hunters vs. Battle Droids|''Bounty Hunters vs. Battle Droids'']].

